title: Salute Winter
description:
Mother Nature is always the boss. She brings us the weather we need to get rad. So as she brings the new winter, Paddy Graham and Julien Lange have decided to honour her with a salute. A salute to winter....

Julien wears the Button up ll jacket: http://eu.oneill.com/en/button-up-ii-...
